    "For instance, the attention score for the title view is computed as:",
    "v∈{t,abs,c,sc} exp(a v) (8) with similar computations for α abs, α c, α sc.",
    "The final unified news representation is the weighted sum across views: r = α t r t + α abs r abs + α c r c + α sc r sc (9) Discussion.",
    "We inherit the multi-view design from NAML due to its interpretability and proven effectiveness in capturing complementary signals from different textual and categorical components of news articles.",
    "Our extensions include (1) replacing shallow word embeddings with BERTbase initialization to better encode contextual semantics, and (2) substituting the original \"body\" with \"abstract\" to reduce redundancy and avoid potential ethical or sensitive content."
